師恩浩蕩　齊頌贊歌 <br />\n感激恩師　培育了我 <br />\n<br />\n如今的我　　懷有抱負 <br />\n能增兵馬　　還望冠軍 <br />\n誰讓贊堅遜　到別處出走 <br />\n師長教導　　成就贊錯 <br />\n<br />\n雲加啊　　是你一顆 <br />\n愛心關懷　燃亮了我 <br />\n兵工～廠　齊頌贊歌 <br />\n感激恩師　培育了我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e6c0dab54083096b6f0e0cc94b22367d8b760f","tid":263973,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:31:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">迷雲黨日漸強大</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b41bcea64bb62265c2f6580c5e9d50a1ac09e2b","tid":263973,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pvxudq9h\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpvxudq9h&h=b37ce86a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a78bd05d20f7cc4b9e6bfaab0bc4899148042663","tid":263973,"uid":16320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/013822_53965e2ef34629f72c31b1522f596d97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F013822_53965e2ef34629f72c31b1522f596d97.jpg&h=7ca33fa2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9a675603e73fa31cbd6b0a0aaae144bf88e763f","tid":263973,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:42:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"134cabcd66a702f6e1a6cdc85a30d3d27b47fbfb","tid":263973,"uid":23752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:57:12.000Z","msg":"入雲我信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8fdcfb384541c78a21fdba2e4ed28a6d01e837b","tid":263973,"uid":3832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:41:27.000Z","msg":"迷雲又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d8d494e3573094af88c60f6805d90e7f9ed40f","ti